For '& Now It's My Life', I took on the role of Technical Director and Lighting Designer.

A major focus of this production was the synergy between the physical stage and the lighting design ; I worked directly with the decor team to build a set that integrated light as a core structural element.

Beyond the creative design, I oversaw the entire technical crew, ensuring that the vision of the director translated to the show and the people behind it.
